114
00:09:29,740 --> 00:09:33,671
Any function of time cannot be
equal to a function of space,

115
00:09:33,671 --> 00:09:34,613
in generality.

116
00:09:34,613 --> 00:09:36,030
It just doesn't make sense.

117
00:09:36,030 --> 00:09:39,765
So each side must be
equal to a constant,

118
00:09:39,765 --> 00:09:41,280
and it's the same constant.

119
00:09:41,280 --> 00:09:45,240
So each side, this is
all equal to a constant.

120
00:09:48,864 --> 00:09:58,530
