144
00:11:45,070 --> 00:11:47,480
It's a first order
differential equation.

145
00:11:47,480 --> 00:11:49,510
Just one function
of integration.

146
00:11:49,510 --> 00:11:52,815
If you guess the answer,
must be the answer.

147
00:11:52,815 --> 00:11:58,070
And that's the time dependence
of a stationary state.

148
00:12:02,480 --> 00:12:08,310
It's exponential
minus iEt over h-bar.

149
00:12:08,310 --> 00:12:10,620
What about the other equation?

150
